OL,3,CMan who filmed himself drink-driving
OL,4,Cbefore crash has sentence increased
OL,6,FA driver who videoed himself admitting
OL,7,Fhe was drunk at the wheel minutes
OL,8,Fbefore killing a woman in a crash has
OL,9,Fhad his prison sentence increased.
OL,11,FAnton Hull was jailed for six years at
OL,12,FTaunton Crown Court in November last
OL,13,Fyear for causing the death of 29-year-
OL,14,Fold Sarah Baker by dangerous driving.
OL,16,FThe collision happened near Wincanton
OL,17,Fin Somerset on 18 August 2022.
