OL,3,CMan who filmed himself drink-driving
OL,4,Cbefore crash has sentence increased
OL,6,FHull, who was 20 at the time,,
OL,7,Fclaiming he was "f****** smashed",
OL,8,Fdespite having been advised not to
OL,9,Fdrink and drive by family members and
OL,10,Fa pub landlord earlier that evening.
OL,12,FThe Attorney General's Office (AGO)
OL,13,Freferred his sentence to the Court of
OL,14,FAppeal, claiming it was "unduly
OL,15,Flenient".
OL,17,FAt a hearing in London on Wednesday 14
OL,18,FFebruary, three appeal judges agreed
OL,19,Fand increased Hull's sentence to one
OL,20,Fof nine years and three months.
