OL,6,FLord Justice William Davis, sitting
OL,7,Fwith Mr Justice Murray and Judge
OL,8,FRobert Altham, said: "He deliberately
OL,9,Fdrove in the teeth of the advice given
OL,10,Fto him by those with his best
OL,11,Finterests at heart.
OL,13,F"We are satisfied that that sentence
OL,14,Ffell outside of the reasonable range
OL,15,Fof sentence available to the judge.
OL,17,F"We quash the sentence of six years of
OL,18,Fimprisonment and substitute in its
OL,19,Fplace a sentence of nine years and
OL,20,Fthree months of imprisonment."
