OL,6,FLord Justice William Davis said Ms
OL,7,FBaker "died instantly" in the
OL,8,Fcollision between her Volkswagen and
OL,9,FHull's Ford Transit van.
OL,11,FThe court heard Hull was believed to
OL,12,Fbe around twice the legal drink-drive
OL,13,Flimit at the time of the crash, with
OL,14,Fthree videos showing him behind the
OL,15,Fwheel of the van later found by police.
OL,17,FThe judge who sentenced him said his
OL,18,Factions were "unbelievably selfish".
