OL,6,FSarah Przybylska, representing the
OL,7,FAGO, said Hull had consumed "multiple
OL,8,Fpints of lager and rum" on the night
OL,9,Fof the incident and had been refused
OL,10,Fservice before the collision, but had
OL,11,Fnot shown remorse.
OL,13,FShe said: "He maintains even now that
OL,14,Fhe was not driving on the wrong side
OL,15,Fof the road.
