OL,6,F"He was sorry someone had died. It was
OL,7,Fnot remorse in the sense of an
OL,8,Fadmission of responsibility, it was
OL,9,Fthe sympathy of someone to a fellow
OL,10,Fvictim of the same unfortunate
OL,11,Faccident.
OL,13,F"He was injured through his own
OL,14,Fseriously culpable conduct."
OL,16,FFollowing Hull's sentencing last year,
OL,17,FMs Baker's family said her death had
OL,18,Fleft a "gaping hole in our hearts" and
OL,19,Fcaused "immeasurable pain".
