OL,6,FThey said: "She was the most caring,
OL,7,Floyal and generous daughter, sister,
OL,8,Fniece, cousin, friend and most
OL,9,Frecently aunty anyone could hope to
OL,10,Fhave in their lives."
OL,12,FHull, who is now 22, suffered a
OL,13,Fshattered femur and dissected aorta in
OL,14,Fthe collision and has since been
OL,15,Fsuffering from post-traumatic stress
OL,16,Fdisorder, his barrister, Patrick
OL,17,FMason, told Wednesday's hearing.
OL,19,FHe had previously worked as a thatcher
OL,20,Fand had hoped to become a professional
OL,21,Fboxer, Mr Mason added.
